{"tid":749361,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"俄羅斯大舉拋售美國國債","createTime":"2018-07-20T03:24:48.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-20T05:54:11.000Z","uid":60545,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"e09176ea1ae9b5c2415b99642af4e8b388bd2c16","tid":749361,"uid":60545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T03:24:48.000Z","msg":"《金融時報》報導，由於美國加重對俄羅斯制裁，使俄國在4、5月大舉拋出美國公債，持有的公債量從原本的近1,000億美元銳減至不到150億美元，意味俄國不再是美國公債最大持有國之一。<br />\n<br />\n根據美國官方本周公布資料顯示，俄羅斯5月出脫140億美元的美長期公債，代表俄方持有的美國公債遠低於3月底將近1,000億美元的水準。<br />\n<br />\n此為俄羅斯連續第2個月拋出美國公債，截至5月底，該國持有公債價值僅149億美元。<br />\n<br />\n(工商 )<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.chinatimes.com/realtimenews/20180719004700-260408\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.chinatimes.com%2Frealtimenews%2F20180719004700-260408&d=UZACy8ioDmpAs2uy0tT7%2Bb%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=16dc35c0\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.chinatimes.com/realtimenews/20180719004700-260408</a>"},{"pid":"6466ec4ab4e0c5fb2503524d712b061f2b622122","tid":749361,"uid":156652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T03:25:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/20/112514_36105b9da753752909fc023732e1f98a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F20%2F112514_36105b9da753752909fc023732e1f98a.gif&h=169d7863&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0f812ef9734c95f61fcae7729ecbb4fb5d13ba1b","tid":749361,"uid":130105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T03:25:39.000Z","msg":"就爆<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41e5678ff67abd8b5f79dc29f63bf734849e6e39","tid":749361,"uid":53577,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"e09176ea1ae9b5c2415b99642af4e8b388bd2c16","tid":749361,"uid":60545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T03:24:48.000Z","msg":"《金融時報》報導，由於美國加重對俄羅斯制裁，使俄國在4、5月大舉拋出美國公債，持有的公債量從原本的近1,000億美元銳減至不到150億美元，意味俄國不再是美國公債最大持有國之一。<br />\n<br />\n根據美國官方本周公布資料顯示，俄羅斯5月出脫140億美元的美長期公債，代表俄方持有的美國公債遠低於3月底將近1,000億美元的水準。<br />\n<br />\n此為俄羅斯連續第2個月拋出美國公債，截至5月底，該國持有公債價值僅149億美元。<br />\n<br />\n(工商 )<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.chinatimes.com/realtimenews/20180719004700-260408\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.chinatimes.com%2Frealtimenews%2F20180719004700-260408&d=UZACy8ioDmpAs2uy0tT7%2Bb%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=16dc35c0\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.chinatimes.com/realtimenews/20180719004700-260408</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T03:25:43.000Z","msg":"1000億美元<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"701a24279b1286325df4bdc52173604fa38cb739","tid":749361,"uid":63669,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T03:26:59.000Z","msg":"入貨先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f836a633967170c5bc7acc8c4317dc5d49e9c70b","tid":749361,"uid":3241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T03:27:15.000Z","msg":"支那接左貨未"},{"pid":"43026d5998ea70d45512fbf23b719e3c548fc0e9","tid":749361,"uid":511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T03:27:17.000Z","msg":"支共仲唔你契哥機<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67875f3c538b268c7ba7a8200487cc9dfbff963e","tid":749361,"uid":511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"43026d5998ea70d45512fbf23b719e3c548fc0e9","tid":749361,"uid":511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T03:27:17.000Z","msg":"支共仲唔你契哥機<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T03:27:47.000Z","msg":"跟"},{"pid":"3ea7779ca95c412261339d1bc7057b97794c5ccc","tid":749361,"uid":14918,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T03:27:49.000Z","msg":"18/07/2018 10:44<br />\n《外地經濟》俄羅斯不在５月美債持倉名單上，中國日本續增持美債<br />\n<br />\n　　《經濟通通訊社１８日專訊》美國財政部公布，外國投資者５月買入美債，當中又以私人投資者為首，因在貿易及意大利政局動盪下，投資者尋求安全資產。　　<br />\n<br />\n不過俄羅斯５月已不在財政部的持倉名單中，先前數據顯示俄羅斯４月美債持倉已從３月的９６１億美元大幅降至４８７億美元。　　<br />\n<br />\n海外投資者５月買進２６６﹒９億美元的美債，４月及３月分別凈賣出４７﹒８億美元及４９﹒２億美元。當中私人投資者５月買入５０２﹒８億美元，抵消外國官方機構賣出的２３８億美元。　　<br />\n<br />\n中國及日本在５月均增持美債，中國的美債持倉量從４月的１﹒１８２萬億美元增至１﹒１８３萬億美元，日本則從１﹒０３１萬億美元增至１﹒０４９萬億美元。（ｍｎ）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.etnet.com.hk/mobile/tc/news/categorized_news_detail.php?category=latest&amp;newsid=ETN280718237\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.etnet.com.hk%2Fmobile%2Ftc%2Fnews%2Fcategorized_news_detail.php%3Fcategory%3Dlatest%26newsid%3DETN280718237&d=UZACy8ioDmpAs2uy0tT7%2Bb%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=665c16c2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.etnet.com.hk/mobile/tc/news/categorized_news_detail.php?category=latest&amp;newsid=ETN280718237</a>"},{"pid":"9142b5a96f0082c7e93eb899e53da812dae50917","tid":749361,"uid":49359,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T03:52:01.000Z","msg":"俄國唔賣邊有錢"},{"pid":"9b3807309dbad3c7e05ff3de68c9c28b602b4f7c","tid":749361,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T03:53:33.000Z","msg":"做壞個市<br />\n支那想賣要大減價"},{"pid":"529fa4b4d7e5b1a44d54b0187a90581de51c5c99","tid":749361,"uid":64073,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T03:57:20.000Z","msg":"俄爆<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"298089534eb5fb02771804721d2563fe1d88590e","tid":749361,"uid":47112,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T03:57:35.000Z","msg":"有冇平貨接吓"},{"pid":"132d5d5dba53e6c6ab228e44fac2bf05d922b299","tid":749361,"uid":55913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T04:00:47.000Z","msg":"普京換d美金洗下"},{"pid":"f282e7d5f1cf41e8f89ba6a0a9570cd4dc9eae50","tid":749361,"uid":193555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime"